keep a secret.

41:51.409 --> 41:53.579
The light blue
is very...

41:53.712 --> 41:55.413
Heteronormative.

41:55.547 --> 41:58.383
I was going to say pastel.

41:58.516 --> 42:00.451
But, yes, that too.

42:00.586 --> 42:03.589
I think he's gonna like
something in the gray palette.

42:03.722 --> 42:05.523
Calming but warm.

42:05.657 --> 42:08.159
Elegant yet understated.

42:10.729 --> 42:14.165
I think our son
